'''Oxonmoot 2023''', the 50th annual [[Oxonmoot]] hosted by [[The Tolkien Society]], took place between [[31 August]] - [[3 September]] [[2023]]. As in the previous years, it was a hybrid event bringing together online delegates with those attending in person at St Ann's College, [[University of Oxford|Oxford]].
